</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>銀河系最大黑洞相片公開，人馬座 A*外型似冬甩</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/14/sagittarius-a/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=sagittarius-a</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 14 May 2022 04:52:23 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[M87]]></category><category><![CDATA[人馬座 A*]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1099909</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>臺灣中央研究院的事件視界望遠鏡（Event Horizon Telescope, EHT）計劃自 2019 年 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>臺灣中央研究院的事件視界望遠鏡（Event Horizon Telescope, EHT）計劃自 2019 年發布首張黑洞相片後，近日再公開銀河系內最大黑洞「人馬座 A*」的相片。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sag_event_image.0.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099969" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sag_event_image.0-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sag_event_image.0-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sag_event_image.0-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sag_event_image.0.jpg 920w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/distance_compare.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099970" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/distance_compare-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/distance_compare-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/distance_compare-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/distance_compare.jpg 920w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>是次公開的人馬座 A* 相片由中央研究院及共 6 所國際著名研究機構共同發布。雖然人馬座 A* 較 2019 年所拍到的黑洞 M87 小 2,000 倍，但距離亦近 2,000 倍，是現存銀河系內最大的黑洞。<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.08.47.png"><br /></a></p><p>中央研究院天文及天文物理研究所博士郭駿毅稱，由照片可推測出人馬座 A* 的直徑約 6,000 萬公里，相當於 43 顆太陽或 4,687 個地球打橫排列。而透過比較 M87 及人馬座 A* 的照片可見，兩者外型呈環狀，與冬甩相似，估計所有黑洞都有相似的外型。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.42.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099963" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.42-694x348.png" alt="" width="694" height="348" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.42-694x348.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.42-1280x642.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.42-768x385.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.42-1536x771.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.42-2048x1028.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.42.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.27.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099962" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.27-694x348.png" alt="" width="694" height="348" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.27-694x348.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.27-1280x642.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.27-768x385.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.27-1536x771.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.27-2048x1028.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.27.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：影片截圖</p><p>雖然距離地球約 27,000 光年的人馬座 A* 較距離 5,500 萬光年的 M87 近，但由於人馬座 A* 的氣體擾動迅速，質量約為太陽的 400 萬倍，令拍照的難度大增。人馬座 A* 的照片是透過收集多項訊號數據，經過多次世界各地的超級電腦模擬、調校而成，共花費 5 年才得出成照。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.10.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099961" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.10-694x348.png" alt="" width="694" height="348" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.10-694x348.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.10-1280x642.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.10-768x385.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.10-1536x771.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.10-2048x1028.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/截圖-2022-05-13-11.09.10.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：影片截圖</p><p>美國史都華天文臺暨亞歷桑那大學天文系及資科所的 EHT 科學家陳志均表示，M87 及人馬座 A* 四周的氣體的移動也近乎光速，氣體圍繞 M87 一圈需約數天至數週，而人馬座 A* 卻小近 2,000 倍，氣體的移動速度因此較 M87 快，令拍照的難度大增。由於人馬座 A* 的氣體移動很快，陳志均形容拍人馬座 A* 照片就如拍一隻追著自己尾巴跑的小狗。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_89703"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/tYUTIXf5zn0?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>資料來源： <a href="https://www.theverge.com/2022/5/12/23042995/black-hole-image-event-horizon-telescope-sagittarius-a-milky-way">The Verge</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
