</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【發佈會】Sonos Ray 正式發佈　入門定價迎合細尺寸電視需要</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/05/14/sonos-ray-launched/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=sonos-ray-launched</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Edward]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 14 May 2022 04:40:03 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[影音產品]]></category><category><![CDATA[ray]]></category><category><![CDATA[Sonos]]></category><category><![CDATA[SoundBar]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1099870</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Sonos 可說是近年冒起甚快的美國音響品牌，以推出智能喇叭聞名。近日 Sonos 就再為旗下 soundba [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Sonos 可說是近年冒起甚快的美國音響品牌，以推出智能喇叭聞名。近日 Sonos 就再為旗下 soundbar 系列多添一位新成員，就是全新發佈的 Sonos Ray。究竟有甚麼特別？就讓 Edward 為大家介紹一下。</p><h2>更細尺寸適合細尺寸電視</h2><p>之前 Sonos 已先後推出 Arc 及 Beam 兩個系列的 soundbar，不過對於 55 吋式以下的智能電視，以及家居較細的家庭來說，這兩款 soundbar 可能仍嫌大了一點。今次 Sonos 推出的 Ray，就十分適合香港家居使用。它在體積上比 Arc 及 Beam 都要短，而且它採用前向發音設計，所以無論是放在電視櫃面、上牆安裝、甚至要塞進組合櫃的小格內，對音效上亦無任何影響，如果再配合 55 吋左右的細尺寸智能電視使用，就更加是最佳搭配。而設計上，它仍然保留傳統 Sonos soundbar 的黑、白兩色設計，走簡約路線，無論是配襯任何類別的家居設計，都十分適合。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos-soundbars-white-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099879" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos-soundbars-white-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos-soundbars-white-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos-soundbars-white-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos-soundbars-white-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos-soundbars-white-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos-soundbars-white-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos-soundbars-white-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲相比 Arc（左）及 Beam Gen 2（中），Ray（右）在體積上確實更細。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Lifestyle-Black-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099876" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Lifestyle-Black-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Lifestyle-Black-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Lifestyle-Black-1-1280x854.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Lifestyle-Black-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Lifestyle-Black-1-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Lifestyle-Black-1.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_024.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099877" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_024-694x391.png" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_024-694x391.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_024-1280x721.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_024-768x433.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_024.png 1400w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_025.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099878" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_025-694x391.png" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_025-694x391.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_025-1280x721.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_025-768x433.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_025.png 1400w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲體積細小，加上採用前向發音設計，擺位上比 Arc 及 Beam Gen 2 更具彈性，而且更適合與 55 吋之類細尺寸電視配合使用。</p><h2>音質不比其他系列遜色</h2><p>至於規格上，Ray 同樣設有兩組高音單元及兩組中音單元，更設有四組 Class-D 數碼放大晶片，這個發聲單元規格，對於家居空間不算大的香港家庭來說已是十分夠用。當然，它亦支援 Sonos 自家的 Trueplay 調音功能，用家可按房間大細及設計，將喇叭音色調校至最佳效果。另外，與其他 Sonos soundbar 一樣，它亦可與其他 Sonos 喇叭，例如：Sonos One、Sub 等組合成一套完整的 5.1 聲道家庭影院，亦可透過 Sonos APP 將喇叭連上 Wi-Fi 網絡，做到與其他房間的 Sonos 喇叭作同步串流播放，功能上不會因為它的定位較低而被比下去。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_028.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099883" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_028-694x391.png" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_028-694x391.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_028-1280x721.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_028-768x433.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_028.png 1400w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>未支援 Dolby Atmos + 語音操控</h2><p>當然，與 soundbar 其他系列相比，Ray 定價較便宜，自然在功能上也有所犧牲。除了音箱體積較細外，它亦未有支援之前加入至 Arc 及 Beam Gen 2 的 Dolby Atmos 音效，只能支援 Dolby Digital 5.1 或 DTS Digital Surround。另外，Alexa / Google 助手的語音操控功能亦未有加入到 Ray 上，操控只能透過 Sonos APP 或喇叭上的輕觸式按鍵。不過 AirPlay 2 無線投放功能，在 Sonos Ray 上仍被保留下來，在發佈會中亦有記者詢問日後能否進一步支援 Google Chromecast，但官方就表示暫時未有此計劃。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Lifestyle-White-6.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099884" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Lifestyle-White-6-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Lifestyle-White-6-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Lifestyle-White-6-1280x854.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Lifestyle-White-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Lifestyle-White-6-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/Lifestyle-White-6.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ray-hero-white-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099886" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ray-hero-white-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ray-hero-white-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ray-hero-white-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ray-hero-white-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ray-hero-white-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ray-hero-white-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ray-hero-white-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ray-back-white-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099885" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ray-back-white-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ray-back-white-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ray-back-white-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ray-back-white-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ray-back-white-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ray-back-white-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ray-back-white-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>6 月中推出定價發佈</h2><p>至於開賣詳情方面，Sonos 宣佈即日起接受預訂 Ray，並會在 6 月 17 日正式推出發售，定價為 $2,999，相比之前的 Arc 及 Beam Gen 2，Sonos Ray 確實十分抵玩，如果大家想初嘗 Sonos soundbar 的效果，Ray 確實是十分不錯的入門款式。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_041.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1099889" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_041-694x391.png" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_041-694x391.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_041-1280x721.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_041-768x433.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sonos_041.png 1400w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
